queries.query: How can I make an appointment with an academic advisor?
queries.response:
To make an appointment with an academic advisor at San José State University, follow these steps:
   1. Log in to MySJSU (<https://mysjsu.sjsu.edu/>) using your credentials.
   2. Click on "Student Services" and then select "Advisement".
   3. Under the "Advising" tab, click on "Schedule an Appointment with Your Advisor".
   4. Choose the college or department that corresponds to your major, and follow the prompts to schedule your appointment.
   5. If you encounter any issues, please visit the Academic Advising Center's website (<https://www.sjsu.edu/advising/>) for additional assistance.

queries.query: How do I apply for on-campus housing?
queries.response:
To apply for on-campus housing at San José State University, follow these steps:
   1. Go to the Housing and Residential Life website (<https://housing.sjsu.edu/>)
   2. Create a MySJSU account if you don't already have one (<https://mysjsu.sjsu.edu/>)
   3. Log in to your MySJSU account
   4. Apply for housing by filling out the online application and submitting any necessary documents
   5. Pay the housing application fee if applicable
   6. Check your MySJSU account for updates on your housing status

If you'd like to learn more about each club or want to get involved, I encourage you to visit their respective websites for additional information and contact details. Here are the links:

   - Society of Automotive Engineers (SAE): [http://saesjsu.com/](http://saesjsu.com/)
   - National Society of Black Engineers (NSBE): [https://nsbe-sjsu.org/](https://nsbe-sjsu.org/)
   - Society of Hispanic Professional Engineers (SHPE): [http://shpe-sjsu.org/](http://shpe-sjsu.org/)
   - Tau Beta Pi (engineering honor society): [https://taubetapi.sjsu.edu/](https://taubetapi.sjsu.edu/)
